name: 30 AMAZING TAKEOFFS AND LANDINGS! Vancouver International Airport Plane Spotting
description:
An amazing full day of December plane spotting at Vancouver International Airport last week, featuring some new additions to the lineup like Singapore Airlines, Qantas, and Air Canada Cargo's first 767F!
